      "description": "Solid fair-condition vehicle that runs and drives as it should, but it shows normal age and use throughout. Expect visible cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, including small dings, scuffs, surface blemishes, and general signs of ownership. It presents respectably overall and should make a good driver for someone looking for a usable car rather than a showpiece.",
