    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a solid opportunity for a handy buyer, first-time owner, or anyone seeking low-cost transportation with upside. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but offers honest value at an accessible price point. If you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive car with potential, this one deserves a look.",
