    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car is being sold in poor condition, so it\u2019s best suited for someone handy, a project-minded owner, or anyone needing a budget-friendly runabout. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an honest car with good potential at a price that leaves room for repairs or tinkering. If you want something cheap and cheerful with a chance to make it your own, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project with strong mechanical character and plenty of upside for the next owner. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it remains an appealing platform with usable drivability, responsive power delivery, and the kind of straightforward engineering that makes it a great candidate for someone who knows their way around maintenance and light reconditioning. A good fit as a commuter, weekend tinkering project, or parts-saving enthusiast car, with major value in its complete package and honest condition. If you want an affordable entry point into ownership without paying top-tier money, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 6200.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Honest poor-condition sale. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
